## Run auth.http → Login first to populate {{token}}

###
## ─── Combat Status ───
###

### Check combat status
GET {{host}}/combat/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Combat Actions ───
###

### Attack with equipped weapon
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "attack"
}

### Cast a damage spell
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "cast",
  "spellId": "fireball"
}

### Cast a healing spell
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "cast",
  "spellId": "heal"
}

### Use a health potion
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "use_item",
  "itemId": "health-potion"
}

### Use a mana potion
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "use_item",
  "itemId": "mana-potion"
}

### Flee from combat
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "flee"
}

###
## ─── Error Cases ───
###

### Attack when not in combat — should fail (404)
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "attack"
}

### Cast without spellId — should fail (400)
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "cast"
}

### Use item without itemId — should fail (400)
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "use_item"
}

### Invalid action — should fail (400)
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "dance"
}

###
## ─── Trigger Encounter (via travel) ───
###

### Travel through forest (high encounter chance)
POST {{host}}/travel/start
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "destinationX": 80,
  "destinationY": 48
}

### Check travel status — may show encounter
GET {{host}}/travel/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Try to travel while in combat — should fail (409)
POST {{host}}/travel/move
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "direction": "north"
}

### Try to rest while in combat — should fail (409)
POST {{host}}/rest/camp
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}

### Try to shop while in combat — should fail (409)
GET {{host}}/shops/thornhaven
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
